name: Where's Naldo?
description:
where she rlly at tho?

Thank you to Inchou Ryu for making custom music.   This game was made with GBStudio by Chris Maltby.

Movement Keys:  WASD/Arrow Keys

Interaction:  ALT/Z/J

My first game, made for the Mini Jam 30!  I struggled with making creative use of the limitation, but I think it counts.  I hope you get amusement out of this silly walking puzzle game!
